          "contents": "def introduce_sidekick():\n    print(\"Meet Thor\")\n    print(\"Health: \") # Add the sidekick's health stat here\n    print(\"Power: \") # Add the sidekick's superpower here\n\n# Call the function to make it run. Add introduce_sidekick() in the next line of code\n",
